Artist-formatting rules:
- Individual artist: SURNAME FIRSTNAME in capitals, no comma (e.g. "Joni Mitchell" -> "MITCHELL JONI").
- Band/group: full group name in capitals, dropping a leading "The" (e.g. "The Doors" -> "DOORS").
- Multiple artists on one item: separate with a backslash ( \ ).
- Soundtracks/compilations with no single artist: use the glossary marker (e.g. OST).

